snippet.title: Age Of Empires III: Definitive Edition Trailer - Pre-Order Now!
snippet.description:
Age of Empires III: Definitive Edition is coming October 15th, 2020! Pre-order now to prepare your battle stations for the all new 4K graphics, rebuilt 3D assets, a modernized UI, cross-play multiplayer, and fully enhanced soundtrack and audio. In addition to all previously released content, Age III: DE also features two new game modes and two new civilizations exclusive to the Definitive Edition! Pre-order and bundle details: https://www.ageofempires.com/news/age3de-preorder-now-gc2020/

---
